1- Add new user
+++++++++++++++++++++++
https://desertbot.io/blog/raspberry-pi-create-add-user

> Create or add a new user interactively
sudo adduser admin

> Confirm the users home directory
ls /home

> Confirm the users information using lslogins
lslogins -u

> Confirm using getent
getent passwd admin
